    <p class="mb-4">
      Estonia's digital health system is world-class. All medical records are electronic and accessible through the patient portal. Prescriptions are digital—you just give your ID number at the pharmacy. For freelancers with insurance, this digital infrastructure makes navigating healthcare much easier.
